{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 90°C. Line 2 baking trays with baking paper and set aside.","Place white sugar into mixing bowl and mill <nobr>10 sec\/speed 9<\/nobr>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside. Thoroughly clean and dry mixing bowl."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk.<\/strong> Place egg whites and fine salt into mixing bowl and whip <nobr>4 min\/37°C\/speed 3.5<\/nobr>, or until stiff, <strong>without measuring cup.<\/strong> ","Mix <nobr>3 min 30 sec\/speed 3<\/nobr>, slowly adding reserved sugar 1 teaspoon and at time through hole in mixing bowl lid until well combined. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk.<\/strong> ","Transfer mixture into a piping bag with a round nozzle (1 cm) and pipe small merinuges (approx. 45) onto prepared baking trays. Bake for 2½-3 hours (90°C) until meringues make a hollow sound when tapped on the bottom. Turn off oven and leave meringues in oven until completely cold. Serve immediately or transfer into a sealable container to store until use."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["220 g white sugar","4 egg whites, room temperature","1 pinch fine salt"]}],"id":"r83804","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/--9vdvzs6RnI\/XZWqKoB-6DI\/AAAAAAAAfT8\/ZguJikF2hjwMbRAm5DTDmiMYpAUm0TqiQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_EWukp4XBr87t8yvY.png","title":"Meringues","publishedAt":"2015-08-07T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"0.3 g","fat":"0 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"4.9 g","calories":"84 kJ \/ 20 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking trays, baking paper, piping bag with round nozzle (1 cm), bowl, sealable container, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Garnish with whipped cream, crushed pistachio nuts and fresh berries."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","5h","45 portions"]}